description:
The CEO talks about Mrs. Harvey's birthday celebration. What three things would you buy with $100 million? Hurricane Michael is worst storm to hit in a long time. Sheryl Underwood stops by to talk about Kanye West and more. Miss Carla talks about Married to Medicine in Reality Update. A $1.4 million painting is shredded. Are You Smarter Than Tommy? Steve VS Tommy. Today in Closing Remarks, Uncle Steve talks about an award that he received and more.
